data.description: LOCATION, location, location. Walking distance to fair, hospital, stores, parks. 2 spacious bedrooms and 2 bathrooms but also a bonus room for office, dining or 3rd bed. Private garage with an additional parking space outside. Private entrance from outside or from garage to unit (stay out of the rain) Spend time doing the things you love while someone else mows the lawn. Kitchen is open with beautiful skylight for natural lighting and has eating bar plus additional dining space. Gas fireplace for cool winter evenings and high 12 ft ceilings to make unit more spacious. Sit on your covered porch all year long and enjoy the fresh air and solitude on an end unit. Add your own touches to make this adorable condo your home! New roof 2022.
